title: Kiss - Peter Criss - Newton, NJ 24-03-1984 LIVE
description:
1984-03-24 ~ Newton, NJ "Criss/Penridge Alliance"
[Audience]


The Alliance, Peter Criss and Stan Penridge's band, performs at a private function in Newton, NJ,
playing a set of classic R&B hits and 1950/60's Rock 'N Roll standards.
Included is Tossin' And Turnin' from Peter's 1978 solo album.
